# Security baseline

- Use `helmet`; configure CORS with an allowlist (avoid `*` if authenticated).
- Rate-limit auth/OTP endpoints; mitigate brute force.
- Be explicit about `trust proxy` when behind a reverse proxy.
- Never implement custom crypto; use proven libraries for hashing/encryption.
- Ensure input validation + output encoding for anything user-controlled.
